        {
          "reviewTitle": "Excellent, lightweight yet covers well",
          "reviewText": "I am a senior adult woman and a lot of makeup settles into my fine lines and wrinkles and it looks terrible. It's very aging. This skin tint perfecter is very light and more like a tinted moisturizer. I could no longer find it in the local store, so I was elated to find it again. I love this product so much I wore it to my class reunion. Another reunion, our 50th is next summer. If I can find the product then, I will wear it again. It's that good.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2026",
